1. Ova stolica je veoma *udobna*. (This chair is very comfortable.)
2. *Udobno* se smestite i opustite. (Make yourself comfortable and relax.)
3. Noge su mi *udobno* smestene na fotelju. (My legs are comfortably placed on the armchair.)
4. U krevetu mi je *udobno*. (I feel comfortable in bed.)
5. Na aerodromu smo cekali satima, ali smo barem imali *udobne* stolice. (We waited for hours at the airport, but at least we had comfortable chairs.)
6. Ne volim da nosim tesnu odeću, uvek biram *udobniju*. (I don't like wearing tight clothes, I always choose more comfortable ones.)
7. Voz je kasnio tri sata, ali bar smo imali *udobne* sedište. (The train was delayed for three hours, but at least we had comfortable seats.)
8. *Udobnost* je ključna stvar koju tražim u hotelu. (Comfort is the key thing I look for in a hotel.)
9. Ovaj kauč je veoma *udoban*. (This couch is very comfortable.)
10. Nije mi *udobno* da spavam u tuđem krevetu. (I don't feel comfortable sleeping in someone else's bed.)